This was the best game ive ever played in my 20 years of gaming.

The entire game is magnificant from beginning to end.

snippet.textDisplay: from software, I really love this game. I love the world that you guys created and I wish you guys keep doing what you do. recently I heard about people complaining about the difficulties. I kinda understand the game that you guys wanted to make, it takes me around 3 weeks to finish the game and I love every second of it. Please don't succumb and make an easy mode because I will use that mode and I¬†think it will ruin my experience with the game. I like that every boss is a learning experience to improve player understanding of the game but I did felt that u guys are kinda holding back on the difficulty. I hope the sequel you guys go all out since you guys already create a great foundation of a game.
